1 - Modify the external properties file using the corresponding connection to MySQL

spring.datasource.url=jdbc:mysql://mysql:3306/mysql
spring.datasource.username=root
spring.datasource.password=

2 - Modify the docker compose script using the corresponding connection to MySQL

MYSQL_DATABASE: root
MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD: 
3 - Add into maven settings.xml using the corresponding connection to MySQL

<pluginGroups>
	<!-- for docker -->
	<pluginGroup>com.spotify</pluginGroup>
</pluginGroups>

<servers>
	<!-- for pushing -->
	<server>
	  <id>docker-hub</id>
	  <username>pegasusma</username>
	  <password></password>
	  <configuration>
		  <email>hongyu.ma@hotmail.fr</email>
	  </configuration>
	</server>
</servers>

2 - Package command

>mvn clean package docker:build -DpushImage

The images generated id : pegasusma/indexation:0-SNAPSHOT

3 - Docker-compose

>docker-compose up


